---
// Coming-soon-style hero (DESIGN §3.1, slice 11b).
//
// Auth + chat are tabled while the surface gets reworked, so the
// hero no longer collects a goal that routes to /sign-in. The
// page-level Carousel + Waitlist below carry the value-prop and
// the conversion ask.
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1 class="hero__wordmark">nlqdb</h1>
  <p class="hero__lede">Natural-language databases.</p>
  <p class="hero__sub">
    Create one in a word. Talk to it in English. The schema, the engine,
    the indexes, the backups — all invisible. The escape hatch to raw
    SQL stays one click away, always.
  </p>

  <p class="heroinput__note">
    <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    Pre-alpha — Phase 0 shipped, Phase 1 in progress. Join the waitlist below.
  </p>
</section>
